dec $filter_<X>(X*, bool*)

1. Case analysis on X*

  1. Case (% matches pattern [])

    1. If ((bool* matches pattern [])), then

      1. Return []

    1. Else Phantom#9

  2. Case (% matches pattern _ :: _)

    1. (Let X_h :: X_t* be X*)

    2. If ((bool* matches pattern _ :: _)), then

      1. (Let b_h :: b_t* be bool*)

      2. Case analysis on b_h

        1. Case true

          1. Return X_h :: $filter_<X>(X_t*, b_t*)

        2. Case false

          1. Return $filter_<X>(X_t*, b_t*)

    2. Else Phantom#10

