dec $flatten_forUpdateStatementList(forUpdateStatementList)

1. If ((forUpdateStatementList matches pattern ``EMPTY`)), then

  1. Return []

1. Else Phantom#45

2. If ((forUpdateStatementList has type forUpdateStatement)), then

