  2. Return [forUpdateStatement]

2. Else Phantom#46

3. If ((forUpdateStatementList has type forUpdateStatementListNonEmpty)), then

  1. (Let forUpdateStatementListNonEmpty' be (forUpdateStatementList as forUpdateStatementListNonEmpty))

  2. If ((forUpdateStatementListNonEmpty' matches pattern `% , %`)), then

