    1. (Let (struct typeId < _typeParameterIR* > { _fieldTypeIR* }) be (typeDefIR as structTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  5. Case (% has type headerTypeDefIR)

    1. (Let (header typeId < _typeParameterIR* > { _fieldTypeIR* }) be (typeDefIR as headerTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  6. Case (% has type headerUnionTypeDefIR)

    1. (Let (header_union typeId < _typeParameterIR* > { _fieldTypeIR* }) be (typeDefIR as headerUnionTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  7. Case (% has type simpleEnumTypeIR)

    1. (Let (enum typeId { _nameIR* }) be (typeDefIR as simpleEnumTypeIR))

    2. Return typeId

  8. Case (% has type serializableEnumTypeIR)

    1. (Let (enum typeId < _typeIR > { _valueFieldIR* }) be (typeDefIR as serializableEnumTypeIR))

    2. Return typeId

  9. Case (% has type externObjectTypeDefIR)

    1. (Let (extern typeId < _typeParameterIR* , _typeParameterIR'* > ({ _pair<callableId, externMethodTypeDefIR>* })) be (typeDefIR as externObjectTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  10. Case (% has type parserObjectTypeDefIR)

    1. (Let (parser typeId < _typeParameterIR* , _typeParameterIR'* > ( _parameterIR* )) be (typeDefIR as parserObjectTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  11. Case (% has type controlObjectTypeDefIR)

    1. (Let (control typeId < _typeParameterIR* , _typeParameterIR'* > ( _parameterIR* )) be (typeDefIR as controlObjectTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  12. Case (% has type packageObjectTypeDefIR)

    1. (Let (package typeId < _typeParameterIR* , _typeParameterIR'* > { _typeIR* }) be (typeDefIR as packageObjectTypeDefIR))

    2. Return typeId

  13. Case (% has type tableObjectTypeIR)

    1. (Let (table typeId { _tableMetadataStructTypeIR }) be (typeDefIR as tableObjectTypeIR))

    2. Return typeId

