dec $update_mode_tbl(TBLC, tableKeyIR*)

1. (Let b_pri be $requires_priority(tableKeyIR))*

2. Case analysis on $exists_(b_pri*)

  1. Case true

    1. Return TBLC[mode = (pri)]

  2. Case false

    1. (Let b_lpm be $is_lpm_key(tableKeyIR))*

    2. (Let tableKeyIR'* be $filter_<tableKeyIR>(tableKeyIR*, b_lpm*))

    3. If ((tableKeyIR'* matches pattern [ _/1 ])), then

      1. (Let [tableKeyIR_lpm] be tableKeyIR'*)

      2. (Let (typedExpressionIR # _nameIR : text _annotationList ;) be tableKeyIR_lpm)

      3. If ((text = "lpm")), then

        1. (Let typeIR be $type_of_typedExpressionIR(typedExpressionIR))

        2. (Let typeIR' be $unroll_aliasType(typeIR))

        3. If ((typeIR' has type integerTypeIR)), then

          1. (Let integerTypeIR be (typeIR' as integerTypeIR))

          2. (Let nat? be $width_of_integerTypeIR(integerTypeIR))

          3. If ((nat? matches pattern (_))), then

            1. (Let ?(n) be nat?)

            2. Return TBLC[mode = (lpm n)]

          3. Else Phantom#585

        3. Else Phantom#586

      3. Else Phantom#587

    3. Else Phantom#588

    4. If (~$exists_(b_lpm*)), then

      1. Return TBLC[mode = (none)]

    4. Else Phantom#589

