    3. Case analysis on prefixedNameIR'

      1. Case (% = prefixedNameIR)

        1. Return ?((parameterIR*, argumentListIR))

      2. Case (% =/= prefixedNameIR)

        1. Return $find_action'(matchAction_t*, prefixedNameIR)

