relation Parameter_ok: p, TC_0, (annotationList direction type name initializerOpt)

1. If ((initializerOpt matches pattern ``EMPTY`)), then

  1. (Type_ok: p TC_0 |- (type as typeOrVoid) : typeIR # typeId_fresh*)

  2. (Let B be $union_set<typeId>($bound(p, TC_0), ({ typeId_fresh* })))

  3. If (Type_wf: B |- typeIR holds), then

    1. (Let nameIR be $name(name))

    2. (Let parameterIR be (annotationList direction typeIR nameIR ?()))

    3. (Let TC_1 be $add_parameter_t(p, TC_0, parameterIR))

    4. Result in TC_1, parameterIR, typeId_fresh*

  3. Else Phantom#1150

1. Else Phantom#1151

2. If ((initializerOpt has type initializer)), then

  1. (Let (= expression_init) be (initializerOpt as initializer))

  2. (Type_ok: p TC_0 |- (type as typeOrVoid) : typeIR # typeId_fresh*)

  3. (Let B be $union_set<typeId>($bound(p, TC_0), ({ typeId_fresh* })))

  4. If (Type_wf: B |- typeIR holds), then

    1. (Expr_ok: p TC_0 |- expression_init : typedExpressionIR_init)

    2. (Let typeIR_init be $type_of_typedExpressionIR(typedExpressionIR_init))

    3. If (((ctk) = $ctk_of_typedExpressionIR(typedExpressionIR_init))), then

      1. (Let typedExpressionIR? be $cast_unary(typedExpressionIR_init, typeIR))

      2. If ((typedExpressionIR? matches pattern (_))), then

        1. (Let ?(typedExpressionIR_init_cast) be typedExpressionIR?)

        2. (Let nameIR be $name(name))

        3. (Let parameterInitializerIR be ((= typedExpressionIR_init_cast) as parameterInitializerIR))

        4. (Let parameterIR be (annotationList direction typeIR nameIR ?(parameterInitializerIR)))

        5. (Let TC_1 be $add_parameter_t(p, TC_0, parameterIR))

        6. Result in TC_1, parameterIR, typeId_fresh*

      2. Else Phantom#1152

    3. Else Phantom#1153

    4. If (((lctk) = $ctk_of_typedExpressionIR(typedExpressionIR_init))), then

      1. (Let typedExpressionIR? be $cast_unary(typedExpressionIR_init, typeIR))

      2. If ((typedExpressionIR? matches pattern (_))), then

        1. (Let ?(typedExpressionIR_init_cast) be typedExpressionIR?)

        2. (Let nameIR be $name(name))

        3. (Expr_eval_lctk: p TC_0 |- typedExpressionIR_init_cast ~> value_init)

        4. (Let parameterInitializerIR be ((= value_init) as parameterInitializerIR))

