        1. (Let integerValue be (value as integerValue))

        2. (Let nat? be $nat_of_integerValue(integerValue))

        3. If ((nat? matches pattern (_))), then

          1. (Let ?(n) be nat?)

          2. Result in (priority = (d (n as int)) :)

        3. Else Phantom#1236

      2. Else Phantom#1237

    3. Else Phantom#1238

