  5. Else Phantom#1275

3. Else Phantom#1276

;; ../../../../../spectec/examples/p4-concrete/5-typing/5.04-typing-relation.spectec:463:1-467:40:
relation Decl_ok: TC_0, declaration

1. Case analysis on declaration

  1. Case (% has type constantDeclaration)

    1. (Let constantDeclaration be (declaration as constantDeclaration))

    2. (ConstDecl_ok: (global) TC_0 |- constantDeclaration : TC_1 constantDeclarationIR)

    3. Result in TC_1, (constantDeclarationIR as declarationIR)

  2. Case (% has type instantiation)

    1. (Let instantiation be (declaration as instantiation))

    2. (InstDecl_ok: (global) TC_0 |- instantiation : TC_1 instantiationIR)

    3. Result in TC_1, (instantiationIR as declarationIR)

  3. Case (% has type functionDeclaration)

    1. (Let functionDeclaration be (declaration as functionDeclaration))

    2. (FuncDecl_ok: (global) TC_0 |- functionDeclaration : TC_1 functionDeclarationIR)

    3. Result in TC_1, (functionDeclarationIR as declarationIR)

  4. Case (% has type actionDeclaration)

    1. (Let actionDeclaration be (declaration as actionDeclaration))

    2. (ActionDecl_ok: (global) TC_0 |- actionDeclaration : TC_1 actionDeclarationIR)

    3. Result in TC_1, (actionDeclarationIR as declarationIR)

  5. Case (% has type errorDeclaration)

    1. (Let (error { nameList }) be (declaration as errorDeclaration))

    2. (Let name* be $flatten_nameList(nameList))

    3. (Let nameIR be $name(name))*

    4. If ($distinct_<nameIR>(nameIR*)), then

      1. (Let nameIR_error be "error." ++ nameIR)*

      2. (Let value_error be ((error . nameIR) as value))*

      3. (Let varTypeIR be (() ((error) as typeIR) (lctk) ?(value_error)))*

      4. (Let TC_1 be $add_vars_t((global), TC_0, nameIR_error*, varTypeIR*))

      5. Result in TC_1, ((error { nameIR* }) as declarationIR)

    4. Else Phantom#1277

  6. Case (% has type matchKindDeclaration)

    1. (Let (match_kind { nameList _trailingCommaOpt }) be (declaration as matchKindDeclaration))

    2. (Let name* be $flatten_nameList(nameList))

