  2. If ((tableKeysPropertyIR'* matches pattern [ _/1 ])), then

    1. (Let [tableKeysPropertyIR] be tableKeysPropertyIR'*)

    2. Return tableKeysPropertyIR

  2. Else Phantom#1792

2. Else Phantom#1793

3. If (([] = $filter_<tablePropertyIR>(tablePropertyIR*, (tablePropertyIR has type tableKeysPropertyIR)*))), then

  1. Return (key = { [] })

